Format Is Memory

‚öñÔ∏è Core Message

Format isn‚Äôt cosmetic ‚Äî it‚Äôs survival. Proper format converts words into court memory.
üìñ Lesson Content

1. Judges navigate by titles and captions ‚Äî not narratives.
2. Numbered paragraphs and double spacing aid citation and review.
3. Certificates of Service convert delivery into legal proof.
4. A clean title (e.g., Notice, Motion) forces clerical recognition.
